column5: It took a bit, but Terry got him some nice fish today. Well done buddy. I knew it was only a matter of time.       Who needs a net? NOOOOOOOOOOOOOTTTTTT TERRY
lol didnt know I left the game..lol my 2 bass on one lure last weekend didnt do it ?    I decided to test my floater suit it passed the test
When you get two lakers, then we,ll talk.....LOL  LOL@ VIDEO.
Nice smallies! I have the striker hardwater suit,  never had to test it so far luckily.
I think after they get to 5 years people should test them under controlled conditions every year

Cool Video Terry, and nice fish.  Always good to test the floater suit out. I do every year just for the hell of it. They are awkward to swim in for sure. Designed to keep your face out of the water, so swimming on your back is easier.  S.
Nice fish Terry and LMAO at the vid but nice to try it out in the summer
